        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 27,
        "ActionId": 27,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Not until we finish the battle report... What can you tell me about the difference between the Elite Corrupted you fought and our regular enemies, Kamui?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 28,
        "ActionId": 28,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Erm... Capt, feel free to write it down yourselves. You probably knew what it was already when you asked me, so what use is my answer anyway?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 29,
        "ActionId": 29,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: '...I\\'m trying to train you on something other than combat.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 30,
        "ActionId": 30,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Fine. I fought eleven of them, and they didn\\'t act weird or anything.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 31,
        "ActionId": 31,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Chrome is filing the report no Strike Hawk member is willing to do, recording everything that has happened since their mission started.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 32,
        "ActionId": 32,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'By the way, Capt, if you\\'ve been doing that report the whole time, did you write down what\\'s happened recently?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 33,
        "ActionId": 33,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Of course. Everything the Strike Hawk has done is well recorded on this portable terminal, and a copy of it goes to the Ministry of War when we\\'re back on Babylonia.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 34,
        "ActionId": 34,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Why are you asking? Something on your mind?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 35,
        "ActionId": 35,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'I just suddenly realized that it has been quite eventful recently, hasn\\'t it?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 36,
        "ActionId": 36,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'First, it was the infiltration on the Nighter... By the way, we should get a dress that properly fits next time. The one I wore was such a hassle.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 37,
        "ActionId": 37,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Ideally, something that separates the top from the bottom part of the dress. It\\'ll be much easier for me to get out of it.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 38,
        "ActionId": 38,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Does that mean you want to do it again...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 39,
        "ActionId": 39,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 40,
        "ActionId": 40,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'And then it was the battle in the Kowloong Metropolis. Didn\\'t expect that outcome.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 41,
        "ActionId": 41,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'The Ascendants became much more active afterward, and our squad has been forced to stay on Earth for the long haul as well.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 42,
        "ActionId": 42,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'I wish we could convince the Ascendants like how we had done with Kowloong. There wouldn\\'t have been so many sacrifices...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 43,
        "ActionId": 43,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'But that\\'s impossible. As long as the Punishing Virus remains a \"virus,\" nothing about it can be changed.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 44,
        "ActionId": 44,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'But Camu took the... He...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 45,
        "ActionId": 45,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'We can\\'t expect everyone to turn into what he is. And I don\\'t think anyone would want another Transcendant if possible.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 46,
        "ActionId": 46,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Not taking a side is a worrisome stance.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 47,
        "ActionId": 47,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'After that...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 48,
        "ActionId": 48,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'There were those fights that were so epic that they\\'ve changed the world order...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 49,
        "ActionId": 49,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'But we\\'ve survived all of them, relying on our hard work and our companions—hmm, companion?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 50,
        "ActionId": 50,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Kamui', 3: 'What\\'s wrong, Capt?', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 51,
        "ActionId": 51,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Chrome', 3: 'Speaking of companions, I just realized that... Wanshi\\'s not here? Wasn\\'t he with us just a while ago?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 52,
        "ActionId": 52,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 53,
        "ActionId": 53,
        "NextActionId": null,
